ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I appreciated the lively conversation, inspired by J.D. and supported by the small, committed group that we were fortunate enough to have. I would recommend this course to those interested in the subject or the method.
See Question 1. I would recommend Professor Connor to other students, but not necessarily this course as currently devised.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I was given the opportunity to write on film journalism in the 1910's, which is a major research project of mine. So, yes, this course allowed me develop my knowledge on a topic that is very important to me.
